{
  "_id": "W3zMIGXwf5LmObd4",
  "name": "Gift of Will",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/violet_26.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A small portion of the mesmerist’s vast mental power buttresses his ally’s mind. The mesmerist can trigger this trick when the subject attempts a Will saving throw or a Sense Motive check, or is targeted by an Intimidate check to demoralize her. For a saving throw, the subject uses the mesmerist’s Will saving throw bonus instead of her own.</p>\n<p>For a Sense Motive check or Intimidate check, she adds the mesmerist’s Charisma bonus as a morale bonus on the check or to the DC. The mesmerist can’t implant this trick on himself.</p>"
    },
